The '''Nathan Reingold Prize''' (formerly Ida & Henry Schuman Prize) is given every year to a [[Postgraduate education|graduate student]] for having written an original [[essay]] in the [[history of science]]. It is awarded by the [[History of Science Society]].<ref name="HSS">{{cite web |url=http://hssonline.org/about/honors/nathan-reingold-prize |title=The History of Science Society: The Nathan Reingold Prize (Formerly Ida & Henry Schuman Prize)|accessdate=2016-11-28}}</ref>
